<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font face="arial" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Thank you for getting in touch with Kingsbridge.<br></span><br style="font-family: arial;"><font face="arial" style="font-family: arial;">We are writing to confirm that, as per your request,&nbsp;</font><b style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">we have cancelled your insurance policy&nbsp;<i>(insert policy number)</i></b><font face="arial" style="font-family: arial;">&nbsp;with Kingsbridge.</font><br style="font-family: arial;"><br style="font-family: arial;"><font face="arial" style="font-family: arial;">To confirm,&nbsp;<b>your policy was active for the period&nbsp;<i>(DDMMYYYY to DDMMYYYY)</i></b>.&nbsp;<br></font><br style="font-family: arial;"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br><b>Cancelling your payment</b><br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">As you were paying for your policy via Direct Debit, we have contacted Close Brothers to ask them to cancel your direct debit as of the above date. They will write to you with confirmation of this, but please be assured that no money is owed for this policy going forward.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br>As a payment is currently in progress, we need to wait until this has been completed before we process your refund. Within 10 to 15 working days this refund will be credited to the account from which you made your Direct Debit payments.<br><br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br><b>Making a claim</b><br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br><i>(Remove mention of Professional Indemnity if policy does not include PI)&nbsp;</i>Any claims submitted for the Professional Indemnity and Goods and Tools Cover elements of the policy will not be met as these operate on a ‘claims made’ basis and therefore the policy must be live in order to respond.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Any claims for the&nbsp;<i>(delete as appropriate)&nbsp;</i>Public Liability, Employers’ Liability, Contract Works, Own Plant and Hired in Plant elements for the time your policy was active&nbsp;can be notified to insurers. Please refer to your policy wording for full information.&nbsp;<br><br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br><font face="arial">If you have any questions regarding the above, please do not hesitate to contact our customer service team on&nbsp;<b>01242 808740</b>.</font><br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br><font face="arial">Kind regards,<br></font></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</a><br style="font-family: arial;"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>